# PII patterns for this workspace
# Each non-empty, non-comment line is a regex matched against staged content.
# Copy this file to .pii-patterns and fill in your own values.

# Atlassian subdomain (e.g. yourname)
# yourname

# ServiceNow PDI hostname (e.g. dev123456\.service-now\.com)
# dev123456\.service-now\.com

# Jira account ID
# [0-9a-f]{24}

# OS username in paths (e.g. /jsmith/)
# /jsmith/
